    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but i literally can't afford to go to the er right now, it's so expensive in sydney and i'm pretty sure i'm just bloated. the pain isn't like \"emergency\" level yet, it's just really uncomfortable. if i just take a couple of codeine tablets and some heat pack, won't that help it pass by morning? i really just need to sleep.",
